snippet.title: Zelda & Chill Trilogy
snippet.description:
The groundbreaking Legend of Zelda lofi / chillhop remix albums by Mikel, Zelda & Chill, Zelda & Chill II, and Zelda & Chill III in one video. Support ‚ñ∏ https://vgm.fm/zeldachill ‚ñ∏ https://vgm.fm/zeldachill2 ‚ñ∏ https://vgm.fm/zeldachill3

Due to the nature of this long video, we could really use your support!  

Videos like this time time and energy to produce, and we do not want to interrupt the music with advertisements. 

Please Save Zelda & Chill 1, 2, and 3 to your favorite music app like Spotify or Apple Music. It supports Mikel and GameChops directly! 

Add your favorite tracks to your playlists, and be sure to share with your friends. This helps new listeners discover our music!

For listeners on Spotify, there are two great playlists
Zelda & Chill (Complete) 
‚Äì All of the GameChops chill beats and lofi albums, like Zelda & Chill. Over 7 hours of music! ‚ñ∏ https://open.spotify.com/playlist/4XKH4rEyBy8kOXSPi3VVno?si=b9e9af17997641f7

Zelda & Chill Trilogy 
‚Äì All of Mikel's Zelda beats, identical tracklist as this video with a bonus track at the end. ‚ñ∏ https://open.spotify.com/playlist/7qy40wjU7mAHWEsB1mESbM?si=7b176e40a931449a

Download / Stream the Zelda & Chill albums
Zelda & Chill ‚ñ∏ https://vgm.fm/zeldachill3
Zelda & Chill 2 ‚ñ∏ https://vgm.fm/zeldachill3
Zelda & Chill 3 ‚ñ∏ https://vgm.fm/zeldachill3

All three Zelda & Chill albums are available on Bandcamp 
‚ñ∏ http://music.gamechops.com

Vinyl records are available on Light in the Attic
‚ñ∏ https://lightintheattic.net/shop-the-catalog?filter%5Blabels%5D=522

~ The History of Zelda & Chill ~ 
In 2018, chill instrumental hip hop producer @MikelTBE  created an album that would inspire a worldwide movement of lofi video game music. The original Zelda & Chill included 14 remixes of The Legend of Zelda video game series. Tracks spanning the original Zelda title theme, to Link to the Past, through Ocarina of Time, Wind Waker, Majora's Mask, and Breath of the Wild. 

Partnering with @DjCutman  for mix and mastering, the two worked together to create the now legendary album Zelda & Chill. The following four years led to the release of Zelda & Chill 2 (2020), and finally Zelda & Chill III (2022). 

The Zelda & Chill Trilogy contains 42 songs and 2 hours of music, all finely produced instrumental hip hop / chillhop / lo-fi style beats from The Legend of Zelda.

With nearly a quarter billion plays on Spotify and over ten thousand vinyl records pressed, Zelda & Chill holds the title as the most popular video game cover album series of all time. 

And it wouldn't be possible without all of the amazing support from our listeners like you. Thanks for listening to Zelda & Chill!

This video featuring gameplay footage by @GreatBitArcade and video editing and visuals by Dj Cutman.
